Package: bigDataAnalyticsTwitter
Type: Package
Title: big_data_analytics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Matthew Schultz
Maintainer: Matthew Schultz <matthewschultz@usf.edu>
Description: The package is designed to helps individuals clean and collect data from twitter.
    It uses a variety of packages to connect with the Twitter API and also provides a customizable 
    way to clean the data.
Imports: httr, jsonlite, tidyverse, plyr, tidytext, readr, stringr, text2vec, tm, qdap, qdapRegex, stopwords, openNLPdata, SnowballC, methods
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
